:"class","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" has been used so as to allow to easily override some attributes and have inheritance, without having for developers","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"to implement all tokens.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Any properties of an overridable theme should be defined so as to provide defaults values.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"We allow this theme to be derivated and be overriden.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/OUDSTheme","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" can be seen as a kind of “abstract class” in ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"object oriented paradigm","type":"text"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":", or ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"theme contract","type":"text"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":".","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Because ","type":"text"},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" is not a ","type":"text"},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"final","type":"text"}]},{"text":" class, its type cannot be seen as ","type":"text"},{"code":"Sendable","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", that is the reason why this conformity is unchecked."}],"type":"topic","kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemescontract\/oudstheme"},"doc://OUDSComponents/documentation/OUDSComponents/OUDSSuggestionChip":{"kind":"symbol","title":"OUDSSuggestionChip","abstract":[{"text":"Suggestion chip is a UI element that allows to present recommended or predictive options based on user’s input or context,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"and is commonly used to capture filtering decisions.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Suggestion chip is typically non-selected by default and can be tapped or clicked to apply the suggestion, streamlining input and enhancing usabili